Assuming populateChangeFeedCache returns a CacheEntry object and isCacheValid takes in the CacheEntry instead of getting again, you could do something like:
CacheEntry cacheEntry = changeFeedCache.get(sessionId);
if (cacheEntry == null || !isCacheValid(cacheEntry, partitionPath, cosmosChangeFeedFindToken)) {
